        <div class="msgSubject">Turning Marauder into a FFXI DRK</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-09-29 06:07:09   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1285762029120908435" id="quote-1285762029120908435" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1285762029120908435" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=176&amp;mid=1285762029120908435&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1285762029120908435&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1285762029120908435" onclick="followToggle('add','1285762029120908435')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
